{
  "texts": [
    "Some statistics comparing our survey to the proposed surveys in the research literature are presented in Table 9.",
    "From this table, we first observe that the most recent survey was proposed in 2019.",
    "However, only 23 recent works from 2015 were described in this survey, which focuses on neural network models proposed for NER.",
    "Also, 15 datasets were presented without being described in detail.",
    "No information about the size, the construction technique, or the location of the presented datasets was given.Concerning the number of the described works, almost all the surveys presented more works than ours."
  ]
}